-- Caterpillar CFO Rapp Says He Expects More Employment
-- B y   S i m o n   C a s e y
-- 2012-02-02T15:09:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-02/caterpillar-cfo-rapp-says-he-expects-more-employment-in-2012.html
(Corrects company name in first paragraph.)  Caterpillar Inc. (CAT)  Chief Financial
Officer Ed Rapp said he expects the company will add more jobs
this year in the U.S.  Growth in U.S. sales of the company’s equipment is being
driven by replacement demand, Rapp said today in an interview
with Betty Liu on Bloomberg Television’s “In the Loop.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
